  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Gather additional efficacy and safety (pharmacovigilance) information in the usual daily care
      in patients with Dyslipidemia on ezetimibe under real conditions in Colombia associated with
      statins.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
