  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  &gt; 18 years old

          -  Lipid Metabolic Disorder as Per ATP III who have not reached the goals and who are on
             statins for at least 4 weeks Or those who require LDL reductions Over 50% to reach the
             ATP III goals or who need statins in accordance their risk score

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnancy, Breast Feeding

          -  Moderate/Sever Liver Disease: Child Score &gt; Or = To 7

          -  Fibrates Terminal Disease

          -  Contraindications To Receive ezetimibe

          -  Contraindications To Receive Statins

          -  Mental Disability

          -  Hypersensitivity To ezetimibe

          -  On another Clinical Research Trial
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
